      *              * Azioni per record non trovato                   *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      "#"                  to   w-let-arc-zdf-flg      .
           move      all   "."            to   w-let-arc-zdf-des      .
           go to     let-arc-zdf-999.
       let-arc-zdf-500.
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
      *              * Normalizzazione work area                       *
      *              *-------------------------------------------------*
           move      spaces               to   w-let-arc-zdf-des      .
       let-arc-zdf-999.
           exit.

